To create the same shape in Python using the turtle library, you can use the following code:

```python
import turtle

t = turtle.Turtle()
t.set_position(0, 0, 0)
t.set_size(100, 100)
t.draw_triangle(100, 50, 0, 140, 50, 0)
t.show()
```
This code sets the turtle's position and size, then draws a triangle with the given coordinates.</s>